                                "en": "It was a wild, <w>lawless</w> territory where the one with the gun ruled."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Жители устали от произвола властей и <w>бессудной</w> жизни в отдалённой провинции.",
                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "The residents were tired of the authorities' arbitrariness and the <w>lawless</w> life in the remote province."
                            }
